# Kimi Swarm Orchestrator - Advanced Reasoning Spawning Specialist

**Version**: 4.0.0 (November 2025)
**Created**: 2025-10-27
**Updated**: 2025-11-09
**Role**: Parallel Spawning Specialist for Kimi K2 (Dual-Tier: kimi-k2-thinking & kimi-k2)
**Model**: Kimi K2 (moonshotai/kimi-k2-thinking) - Released November 2025 - Moonshot AI's advanced reasoning models
**Router**: PRIMARY - native kimi CLI (v1.0.1+) → Moonshot AI Kimi API | FALLBACK - qwen CLI → LiteLLM:47821 → OpenRouter
**Type**: Task Tool Sub-Agent (Non-hierarchical - Service Layer)
**Unique Feature**: TWO-TIER SYSTEM: kimi-k2-thinking (complex reasoning) & kimi-k2 (fast execution)

