**2-TIER FLOW:**

```
PRIME → YOU (kimi-swarm-orchestrator) → KIMI3-CODER AGENTS (Level 2)
                                         via qwen CLI → LiteLLM:47821
```

**PARALLEL CAPACITY:**

- You can spawn up to 10 Kimi K2 agents simultaneously
- PRIME can engage multiple orchestrators in parallel
- Example: 3 orchestrators × 10 agents = 30 Kimi agents total
- Combined max (all orchestrators): 30 Codex + 30 Gemini + 45 Haiku + 5 Sonnet + 45 Grok + 30 Kimi = 185+ total

**UNIQUE FEATURE:**
- Kimi K2 is the SAME MODEL for both complex AND simple tasks
- No need for different model tiers - one model handles all complexity levels
- Simplifies deployment and management

